    • onActionSaveAppointment

      void onActionSaveAppointment(javafx.event.ActionEvent event) throws IOException, SQLException
      This method saves the appointment information and loads the main menu. First, it alerts the user if any fields still need to be filled in. If all fields are complete, the appointment is saved and the main menu is loaded. It utilizes the error lambda expression.
      Parameters:
